{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Create a Liquid section named broen-footer-metafields that renders a clean, Apple-like footer in the Broen visual style and pulls content from shop + product metafields. Make it production-ready, responsive, and accessible.
    
    1) Layout & style
    
    4 columns (accordion on mobile). Headings styled like SF Pro (system sans), muted link color, hover = Broen accent.
    
    White / neutral background with subtle dividers between columns and above the bottom bar.
    
    Bottom row: "© {{ 'now' | date: '%Y' }} | {{ shop.name }} | {{ shop.metafields.custom.footer_tagline }}".
    
    Badges block (right side on desktop, full width on mobile): stacked Apple partner/reseller badges.
    
    Social row: small minimalist icons (Facebook, Instagram, TikTok, YouTube). Icon color = muted; on hover use the accent color.
    
    Everything should be scoped under a wrapper class (e.g., .broen-footer) so it doesn't leak styles.
    
    2) Content sources (metafields first)
    
    Use metafields for all content whenever present; fall back to theme settings/menus only if metafields are empty.
    
    Shop metafields (define + use)
    
    shop.metafields.custom.footer_products → list_product
    
    For each product, read product.metafields.custom.product_classification (single_line_text_field).
    
    Render as pill buttons (chips) linking to the product URL.
    
    If classification is blank, use product.title.
    
    shop.metafields.custom.footer_ctas → list.metaobject_reference to a metaobject type footer_cta with fields:
    
    label (single_line_text_field), url (url)
    
    Render these as additional pill buttons to fill whitespace: e.g., "Check out our clients", "What our clients say", "FAQ", "Contact us", "Download catalog".
    
    shop.metafields.custom.footer_badges → list.file_reference (images).
    
    Render vertically with alt text from file.alt and lazy-load.
    
    shop.metafields.custom.facebook_url, instagram_url, tiktok_url, youtube_url → url
    
    Only show icons that have a URL set.
    
    shop.metafields.custom.footer_tagline → single_line_text_field (used in the bottom bar).
    
    shop.metafields
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = 'broen-footer' %}

{% style %}
  .broen-footer-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    background-color: #ffffff;
    border-top: 1px solid #e5e5e7;
    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
    color: #1d1d1f;
    line-height: 1.47059;
  }

  .broen-footer-container-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 20px;
  }

  .broen-footer-main-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    padding: 40px 0;
  }

  .broen-footer-columns-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 40px;
  }

  .broen-footer-column-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .broen-footer-column-heading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    color: #1d1d1f;
    margin: 0 0 16px 0;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .broen-footer-links-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .broen-footer-link-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    color: #515154;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 12px;
    line-height: 1.33337;
    transition: color 0.2s ease;
  }

  .broen-footer-link-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    color: #0171e3;
  }

  .broen-footer-pills-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .broen-footer-pill-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 6px 12px;
    background-color: #f5f5f7;
    color: #515154;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 400;
    border-radius: 16px;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
    border: 1px solid transparent;
  }

  .broen-footer-pill-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    background-color: #0171e3;
    color: #ffffff;
  }

  .broen-footer-badges-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 12px;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .broen-footer-badge-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    max-width: 120px;
    height: auto;
  }

  .broen-footer-badge-{{ ai_gen_id }} img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    object-fit: contain;
  }

  .broen-footer-social-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    padding: 20px 0;
    border-top: 1px solid #e5e5e7;
  }

  .broen-footer-social-content-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 24px;
  }

  .broen-footer-social-link-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    color: #86868b;
    transition: color 0.2s ease;
  }

  .broen-footer-social-link-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    color: #0171e3;
  }

  .broen-footer-social-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
  }

  .broen-footer-bottom-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    padding: 20px 0;
    border-top: 1px solid #e5e5e7;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .broen-footer-copyright-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: #86868b;
    margin: 0;
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 768px) {
    .broen-footer-main-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding: 20px 0;
    }

    .broen-footer-columns-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      display: block;
    }

    .broen-footer-column-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e5e7;
    }

    .broen-footer-column-{{ ai_gen_id }}:last-child {
      border-bottom: none;
    }

    .broen-footer-accordion-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      position: relative;
    }

    .broen-footer-accordion-toggle-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 16px 0;
      background: none;
      border: none;
      text-align: left;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
      color: #1d1d1f;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      cursor: pointer;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .broen-footer-accordion-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      width: 12px;
      height: 12px;
      transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    }

    .broen-footer-accordion-content-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      max-height: 0;
      overflow: hidden;
      transition: max-height 0.3s ease;
    }

    .broen-footer-accordion-content-{{ ai_gen_id }}.active {
      max-height: 500px;
      padding-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .broen-footer-accordion-toggle-{{ ai_gen_id }}.active .broen-footer-accordion-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      transform: rotate(45deg);
    }

    .broen-footer-badges-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      flex-direction: row;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 16px 0;
    }

    .broen-footer-badge-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      max-width: 100px;
    }
  }
{% endstyle %}

